high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
pick up the red cloth on the counter.
Move to your left in front of the sink.
Put the red cloth in the sink to run water over it and then pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the bath tub.
Place the wet red cloth in to the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Place one red wet cloth in to the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the tub, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the dirty red rag off of the counter.
Put the dirty rag in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and take out the now clean rag.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the tub.
Put the clean red rag in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean red rag in the tub.

high_descs: move to the counter to the right of the sink
pick up a rag from the counter
move to the sink to the left
clean the rag in the sink
move to the tub to the right
put the rag in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag in the tub.
